Veteran actor, Mike Mvelase, fondly known as 'Khaphela' rocked up at an event wearing the most unexpected outfit. The Matrix looking outfit shows that 'Khaphela' is a bold character on and off screen. The event is hosted today by SABC1 using the hashtag: #SABC1PaintsTheTownRed. Follow the hashtag on twitter to see who whore what! For us, Khaphela takes the trophy. 